# Ignore files/folders in git repositories
#   @see https://git-scm.com/docs/gitignore

# 🗃️ Archives
*.tar.gz
*.tar.bz2
*.gz
*.zip
*.bz2
*.rar



# 🤖 Generated files & folders
build/
dist/
prod/
## Ansible custom generated files
### everything in the generated/ folder..
generated/
### .. except README.md
!generated/README.md
### also ignore everywhere any "-generated" suffixed file
**/*-generated*
### Temporary folder, used for generated WIP, notes or debug
tmp/



# 📄 Logs
logs/
*.log



# 🖥️ OS Specific

## Linux
*~
### KDE directory preferences
.directory
### Linux trash folder which might appear on any partition or disk
.Trash-*

## macOS / OS X
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
**/._.DS_Store
ehthumbs.db
Thumbs.db
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
### Thumbnails
._*

## Windows
### image file caches
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini
### Recycle Bin used on file shares
$RECYCLE.BIN/
### Installer files
*.cab
*.msi
*.msm
*.msp
### shortcuts
*.lnk



# 📦️ Package manager stuff

## Exclude npm/yarn package folders
node_modules/
npm-debug.log
npm-debug.log*
stats.json
### Optional npm cache directory
.npm
### Exclude package manager files
package-lock.json
yarn.lock

## Bower dependency directory (https://bower.io/)
bower_components/

## Composer
vendor/
### Keep public vendors, like ~Bootstrap, Font awesome
!public/assets/vendor/



## 🔒️ Secrets
# Ignore everywhere any "_secret" suffixed file
**/*_secret*

### 🤖 Ansible
#### Real hosts file
hosts
hostsWithCustomSSHPort
#### Real variables file
**/**/vars/main.yml

### WordPress
**/wp-config.php


# 📌 Tests / Unit tests reports
coverage/
tests/coverage*



